    <mxCell id="read-threat" value="&lt;b&gt;Read Threat Surface&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;structured inventory file&lt;br&gt;endpoints, services, data flows&lt;br&gt;credentials, CRDs, trust boundaries&lt;br&gt;RBAC changes, agent/MCP surfaces" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#333333;strokeWidth=2;arcSize=10;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=5;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Inter,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;" vertex="1" parent="1">
